<body lang=EN-GB>

<div class=Section1>

<h2><a name="_Toc76981886"><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;
font-family:Arial'>Student Charter</span></b></a></h2>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify'><b>INTRODUCTION</b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal>&nbsp;</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:12.0pt'>Trinity and All Saints is an
independent Catholic foundation, committed to the principles of care and community. 
It has been offering degrees of the University of Leeds since its inception and
was granted accredited status by the University in 2001.  The College offers a
range of vocationally-oriented undergraduate and postgraduate programmes and
provides continuing professional education in a number of areas including
media, languages and education.</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:12.0pt'>All students have rights,
privileges and obligations as a result of entering into partnership with the
College.  This Charter defines that relationship and serves as the point of
reference by which adherence to or breach of its spirit and content will be
judged. </p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:12.0pt'>This Charter defines the
standards of provision which students can reasonably expect and the
responsibilities they assume as members of the College.  While the College will
strive to achieve the standards as stipulated, their inclusion in this Charter
does not make them legally binding. </p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:12.0pt'> </p>

<p class=MsoNormal><b>CONTRACTUAL LIABILITY</b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal>&nbsp;</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:12.0pt'>Trinity and All Saints undertakes
to take all reasonable steps to provide the teaching, examination, assessment
and other educational provision set out in its Prospectus, Student Handbook and
other official publications.  It cannot, however, guarantee their provision in
all circumstances.  Should events beyond the control of the College interfere
with its ability to operate normally, the College undertakes to minimise the
resultant disruption. The whole of this Charter should be construed
accordingly.</p>

<p class=MsoNormal>&nbsp;</p>

<p class=MsoNormal><b>BEFORE YOU ARRIVE AT COLLEGE</b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><b>&nbsp;</b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:8.0pt'><b>You may expect the College
to:</b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>publish clear, accurate and up-to-date information about academic
provision</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>provide information on College services and facilities including
accommodation, support services, library and IT, sports facilities and the
Student Union</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>operate clear and fair admissions procedures with each application
receiving full and prompt consideration</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><u>encourage</u> applications from students with disabilities and
from those who come from sectors of society under-represented in higher
education</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>publish contact details should you require any further  guidance
on any aspect of the College's provision.</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span
style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>send you clear briefing material prior to registration</p>

<p class=MsoNormal>&nbsp;</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:8.0pt'><b>You are expected to</b>:</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>provide full and accurate information as required by the
admissions process</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>respond to correspondence by specified deadlines and keep interview
appointments</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span
style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>make the best use of information provided to help you make an
informed choice of programme of study, seeking further guidance if required</p>

<p class=MsoNormal>&nbsp;</p>

<p class=MsoNormal>&nbsp;</p>

<p class=MsoNormal><b>AS A REGISTERED STUDENT</b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><b>&nbsp;</b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:8.0pt'><b>You may expect the College
to:</b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>keep accurate records of the information you have provided and of
your academic progress in a manner compliant with the Data Protection Act</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>provide a clear statement of tuition, residence and/or other fees
at the commencement of each session</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><u>make available on an annual basis</u> information about the College
together with academic regulations, details of programmes of study and
individual modules in terms of content and assessment</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>provide good quality teaching delivered in appropriate
accommodation in accordance with published timetables</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>assess your work, and provide you with feedback, in accordance
with published schedules </p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>provide effective and appropriate academic, pastoral and
financial guidance </p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>provide appropriate facilities to support learning, including
library and IT services</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>provide you with opportunities to evaluate your programme of
study and experience as part of the process by which the College maintains and
enhances the quality of its provision</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>provide a congenial, safe and supportive living environment, with
appropriate and well-maintained buildings and grounds</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>provide an environment that <u>promotes equality and diversity</u></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>provide a spiritual environment which is sympathetic to differing
religious beliefs and those who have no religious beliefs</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>provide appropriate support for students with disabilities</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>provide a catering service offering a variety of food and
beverages at reasonable prices</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>comply with Health &amp; Safety legislation</p>

<p class=MsoNormal>&nbsp;</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:8.0pt'><b>You are expected to:</b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>behave in a manner which shows respect for fellow students,
College staff, the community and the physical environment</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>familiarise yourself and comply with College regulations and
other information on your programme of study, seeking clarification on anything
you do not understand</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><u>exercise responsibility for your independent learning and your
personal academic judgement by participating in all classes and examinations as
required by the regulations governing your programme of study and submitting
all coursework as required for your  programme of study</u></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>meet with your Progress Tutor at least twice each year</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>seek guidance and support from appropriate staff if you
experience any problems</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>reply to all correspondence by the specified deadline</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>make use of College facilities and abide by the regulations
specified for their use</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>pay any fees owed to College by the specified deadline</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>make use of the opportunities provided for you to contribute your
views on your student experience</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><u>inform the College of any changes to your contact details</u></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p class=MsoNormal><b>IF THINGS GO WRONG</b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><b>&nbsp;</b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><b>You may expect the College, in consultation with the Student
Union, to:</b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal>&nbsp;</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>explain the consequences of unsatisfactory academic performance</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>publish and operate clear, fair procedures for addressing
complaints, academic appeals, disciplinary matters and allegations of cheating
and plagiarism</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span
style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>provide independent advice, on request, regarding complaints,
appeals, cheating and plagiarism and disciplinary procedures</p>

<p class=MsoNormal>&nbsp;</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>provide advice on the academic and financial implications of
changing programme of study, suspending your studies or withdrawing from the
College</p>

<p class=MsoNormal>&nbsp;</p>

<p class=MsoNormal><b>You are expected to:</b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal>&nbsp;</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>seek advice and follow relevant procedures if you wish to change
programme, suspend studies, leave the College or have a query relating to
complaints, appeals, cheating and plagiarism or disciplinary procedures</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span
style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>familiarise yourself and comply with the appropriate procedure
before submitting a complaint or appeal</p>

<p class=MsoNormal>&nbsp;</p>

<p class=MsoNormal>&nbsp;</p>

<p class=MsoNormal><b>ON COMPLETION OF YOUR STUDY AT THE COLLEGE</b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><b>&nbsp;</b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><b>You may expect the College to:</b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal>&nbsp;</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>provide you with a transcript as evidence of completion of your
programme of study</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>arrange for the conferment of your degree either at a ceremony at
the University of Leeds or <i>in absentia</i></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>provide academic references on request</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span
style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>provide replacement or additional documentation, on request, on
payment of the appropriate published fee</p>

<p class=MsoNormal>&nbsp;</p>

<p class=MsoNormal><b>You are expected to:</b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal>&nbsp;</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>inform the College of your choice of conferment by the specified
deadline</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><span
style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>request references and any supplementary or replacement
documentation in good time</p>

<p class=MsoNormal>&nbsp;</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:12.0pt'><b>TRINITY AND ALL SAINTS
STUDENTS' UNION (TASCUS)</b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:12.0pt'>As a registered full-time College
student you are eligible for membership of the Students' Union.  The Students'
Union currently provides a range of advisory, social, cultural, sporting and
leisure facilities.  The core principle of all Students' Unions is democratic
control by the student membership. </p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:12.0pt'><b>You may expect TASCUS to:</b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:12.0pt'><span
style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>provide information about the Students' Union from Students'
Union officers</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:
12.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>arrange NUS membership and supply an NUS card on payment of the
appropriate fee</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;
margin-left:18.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:12.0pt'><span
style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>allow all registered students to have access to all Students'
Union facilities, clubs and societies</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:12.0pt'><span
style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>invite all members to take part in the democratic processes of
the Students' Union, by attending General Meetings, standing for election to
office in the Students' Union and exercising the right to vote</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:12.0pt'><span
style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>provide confidential advice on matters relating to finance,
housing, welfare, relations with staff or fellow students, academic concerns or
similar issues.</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:
12.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>represent the student body within the College and in the wider
regional and national context</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:12.0pt'><b>You are expected to:</b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:12.0pt'><span
style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>be aware and make use of the various services provided by the
Students' Union</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:
12.0pt'><span style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span>support the democratic life of the Students' Union<b> </b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:12.0pt'><b>&nbsp;</b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:12.0pt'><b>&nbsp;</b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:12.0pt'><b>REVIEW OF THE STUDENT CHARTER</b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:12.0pt'>This Charter shall be reviewed
annually by the Principal and triennially by the Board of Governors.</p>

<p class=MsoNormal>&nbsp;</p>

